Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As for what happens to Ruri the self proclaimed Snow woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good morning, Hiroshi-sama. Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's still in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(1000,0)}http://wakusubs.wordpress.com
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.93,0:00:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is omelette made specially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Omelette?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, and that's strawberry ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But it seems to have melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But they look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This isn't Miso soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's true they look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And so, this is the start of my weird lifestyle living with Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, that's cruelty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Packaging cute cats into boxes and selling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:01:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm getting you all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How can they even fit inside those boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Concealing yourself when the situation turned awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just stay vanished and stop creating anymore trouble, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm hungry. Let's get lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, I have caused trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please take the umbrella, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You'll cause me more trouble if you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How's everything coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You look like you can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do I look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You told me to take care of Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Honestly speaking, I have no idea how to treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's a Snow woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and is clueless about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's not the main issue, rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can't help yourself to look at her like a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I-Idiot! What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why would I treat a Snow woman like Ruri as a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's just lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why are you so flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Probably because I walked in the rain yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can treat Ruri-san as something like a family of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right! A little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama? Hiroshi-sama!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's right. Youko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've seen him talk to Youko-sama with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko-sama! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why isn't she answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What? You only just woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You'll be late if you don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll be back a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It rained earlier than the weather report says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait, you can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't forget your umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't go! You can't go, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}It's just like snow now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}Searching for that lost voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}Stranded on the Plover mountains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}where the snow is falling now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}Putting on lipstick on this kid tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\b1 \i1}for her to take part in the village festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do you feel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My fever seems to have subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's great. Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I have no appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That won't do. You need nutrients after recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm in the midst of preparing porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Was that a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, can you get up? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That sensation on my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It was from Ruri's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She scalded her hand because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I scalded myself while cooking just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My cooking has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The porridge is a delicacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see... I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri is this kind of girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You should hurry and eat, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How's it? Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You mixed up the salt with sugar again, Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This isn't a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is my first time eating sweet porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can used the prickles to adjust at this sort of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This won't change the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Isn't it too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Really? I thought it's rather fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko-sama! Which of these do you think suits me most?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They all suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Really? I'm taking them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't be silly! You're getting only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How about trying them before deciding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What occasion is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You were still fretting over how to treat her not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now you're buying clothes for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She only has a Kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's rather pitiful wearing like a Snow woman everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This isn't too bad, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko-sama. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't decide. Could you pick one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You look great, Ruri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's a reflection of your good taste, Youko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You think? I still feel the ones I chose earlier are better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No. I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What I mean is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's your first time wearing western clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's why you can't tell which designs suit you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's fine. I prefer this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi is gradually becoming who he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right, Youko. You should teach Ruri to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You have no idea. I eat shocking good daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What exactly is shocking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like what's inside Miso soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stop that, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's embarrassing Youko-sama learns of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko-sama, is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, if it's too fine, the floor will get too sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So this should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll go get the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll whip something delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Beware of the splattering oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That works I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The radish is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are we making radish tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No we're not. Grated radish as sauce makes it extra delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Watch the fire while I buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The tempuras should almost be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko! Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where did they go? Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They don't know tempura tastes best when eaten hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then I shall have a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry, I decided to take a shower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,W-W-Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right. Tempura goes well with radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why are you so flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But we love each other so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I love you! But we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anyway, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Weren't you yelling at me to wake up this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So if you have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's almost done. Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-Isn't it cute? \NI thought it was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's mean! This is my voice. When did you record it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When you wake me up every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I tape recorded your voice in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Dubbed: Ruri Alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hear it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's morning. Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wake up! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Geez, it's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Since when do I yell this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right. It's a ogre's voice that spares no one to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I asked Hiroshi to look after Ruri-san so that he becomes outgoing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He is definitely much happier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Full of vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the effect is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see it. It's the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The sea during winter seems melancholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Melancholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Compared to the buzz during summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,the sea during winter is almost deserted making it sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stop flying, Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri, don't float in midair. Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sheesh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I  was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What would you do if I wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Take for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's see... relieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No one to disturb me in the mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I won't eat strange cookings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't have to care about others while watching films.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why am I a Snow woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't I have contact with people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why can't I touch the people I love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not even an embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hate the winter sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's like looking at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hate it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's wrong, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why? Why are you getting in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No! Please leave Hiroshi-sama alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What? What happened, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's someone else in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I managed to suppress it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who knows when it'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Your body is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, hug me. Please hug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I beg you. I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama... I can't anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.19,0:24:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.49,0:25:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm so happy, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.40,0:25:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.05,0:25:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I want to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.77,0:25:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I can't. I'm already at my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.02,0:25:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.85,0:25:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.69,0:25:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll be fine as long as you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.38,0:25:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Farewell, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.49,0:25:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Farewell, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.45,0:26:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.88,0:26:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri? Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.92,0:26:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.73,0:26:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
